data.revised_prompt: Create a photorealistic and professional-grade image of a 'Tropical Sunset Breeze' cocktail. The cocktail is served in a tall, curvaceous hurricane glass hosting a drink that displays a gradient, transitioning from a deep red hue, courtesy of the grenadine, at the base, to a soft golden at the top. The garnishing of this elegant cocktail includes a skewered pineapple slice and a maraschino cherry that enhances its appeal. The glass, lit by warm, golden light that recreates the feel of a setting sun, stands out against a blurred beach backdrop. Subtle reflections are observable on the glass, complementing the vibrant colors of the drink. The setup gives off an aura of tropical charm and captivates the essence of a serene sunset. Background is clear with soft focus and no text or watermarks present.
